    "Furthermore, RELEX offers a promising approach for learners to improve their recipe writing skills by integrating both the learning domain (procedural writing) and the exemplifying domain (cooking).",
    "Despite its effectiveness, its scope is limited to these specific areas.",
    "One main takeaway for the research community is the demonstrated importance of adaptivity and personalization in example-based learning, particularly in enhancing user engagement and performance outcomes.",
    "In future work, the example-selection pipeline can be adapted to cater to other learning domains.",
    "For instance, journal writing (Roelle et al., 2012), high school instruction (Hilbert et al., 2008), or argumentative writing (Schworm & Renkl, 2007)."
